abstract: Visa, which plans to float shares on the New York Stock Exchange on Wednesday in the biggest initial public offering ever in the United States, will not be deterred by market turmoil that has taken a severe toll in recent days, analysts told Reuters on Monday.

headline.main: Visa I.P.O. To Go Ahead, Analysts Say
